{
  "name": "Scenario - Investor Update Prep",
  "steps": [
    {
      "name": "Log CFO's metric rundown",
      "ir": {
  "_comment": "CEO 周一早上先把 CFO 发来的核心经营指标记入系统，邮件里还有 Excel 附件的详细分部数据，这里先抓重点免得准备投资人更新时反复翻邮件。",
        "stage": "ENC",
        "op": "Encode",
        "args": {
          "payload": {
            "text": "Q3 Week 12 指标：ARR 计入 42.6M，同比增长 18%；净留存率 118%；本周新增 3 家企业客户，其中 2 家来自合作渠道。风险：美国区两个续约谈判推迟到 10 月底。"
          },
          "tags": ["investor-update", "metric", "owner:ceo"],
          "type": "executive_note",
          "time": "2025-09-29T08:15:00+08:00",
          "source": "notion_board",
          "facets": {
            "subject": "Q3 Investor Update",
            "topic": "financials"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Retrieve recent investor talking points",
      "ir": {
  "_comment": "准备对比前几周的更新，Notion 页面里还有去年的更新稿，这里先检索最近几周提过的亮点和风险，避免重复对外沟通。",
        "stage": "RET",
        "op": "Retrieve",
        "target": {
          "search": {
            "intent": {
              "query": "investor update talking points",
              "context": "monthly stakeholder email"
            },
            "overrides": {
              "k": 12,
              "order_by": "time_desc"
            },
            "limit": 12
          }
        },
        "args": {
          "include": ["id", "text", "time", "tags", "weight"]
        },
        "meta": {
          "actor": "ceo-office",
          "lang": "en"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Schedule weekly reminder to polish draft",
      "ir": {
  "_comment": "CEO 想在每周一 9 点收到提醒，除了 Calendar 里已有的彩排会议，记忆里加个提醒检查 investor-update 草稿是否更新。",
        "stage": "STO",
        "op": "Promote",
        "target": {
          "filter": {
            "has_tags": ["investor-update", "draft"],
            "limit": 30
          }
        },
        "args": {
          "remind": {
            "rrule": "FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO;BYHOUR=9;BYMINUTE=0;BYSECOND=0",
            "until": "2025-12-01T09:00:00+08:00"
          }
        },
        "meta": {
          "actor": "ceo-office",
          "timestamp": "2025-09-29T08:30:00+08:00"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
